title: 336.9-802 SAVINGS CLAUSE.
text:
(a) Pre-effective date transactions or liens. Except as otherwise provided in this section, Laws 2011, chapter 31, applies to a transaction or lien within its scope, even if the transaction or lien was entered into or created before Laws 2011, chapter 31, takes effect.
(b) Pre-effective date proceedings. Laws 2011, chapter 31, does not affect an action, case, or proceeding commenced before Laws 2011, chapter 31, takes effect.
